data.description: Wow.  Talk about space, comfort and location.  This lovely 3 living area, 3 bedroom, 3 bath and 3 car garage has many custom features.  Vaulted ceilings, arched windows, wonderful detail in the trim, curved stairway and so much more. Main Living Room has soarig ceilings and see thru fireplace. The two main Living areas and Breakfast area have views to the back yard and covered patio. Master Bedroom is large enough for a sitting area, tray ceiling and lovely master bath with Hollywood tub and shower.  Media Room could be many things.  It could be a fabulous office, another bedroom or a huge game room.  It has built in cabinets and wet bar and micro wave - almost a mini Kitchen.  Or it could be a mini retreat. It has an attached patio with wonderful views of the spacious lawn.  Utility room is spacious and has drip dry area and sink.
